OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1773155489
OL,3,CPolice officer denies dismissing
OL,4,Cassault complaint about Nottingham
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FA police officer has denied dismissing
OL,8,Fa complaint made by Valdo Calocane's
OL,9,Fflatmate that the triple killer
OL,10,Fassaulted him following an argument,
OL,11,Fan inquiry heard.
OL,13,FPc Zacharia was one of two officers
OL,14,Fwho responded to reports that
OL,15,FCalocane, then studying mechanical
OL,16,Fengineering at the University of
OL,17,FNottingham, put a student in his
OL,18,Fshared accommodation, Christopher, in
OL,19,Fa headlock on January 15 2022
OL,20,Ffollowing an argument about cleaning
OL,21,Fthe shower.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
