OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1773155489
OL,3,CPolice officer denies dismissing
OL,4,Cassault complaint about Nottingham
OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FCalocane is currently detained
OL,8,Findefinitely in a high-security
OL,9,Fhospital after prosecutors accepted
OL,10,Fhis not guilty pleas to murder at his
OL,11,Fsentencing at Nottingham Crown Court
OL,12,Fin January 2024.
OL,14,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/8
